title: Bee Bowen Young Eucalyptus Medium Scarf
description:
Bee Bowen's silk textiles are an attempt to examine nature’s transient beauty through her designer's creative lens. Each piece is a one-of-a-kind work of art, handcrafted by Bee using locally foraged flora placed on sustainably sourced silk. Due to the unique design and dyeing processes, every piece is different and will vary in composition and color tones.

  • Dimensions: 82 x 20 in.
